5D4E7D6A.Line1.CDDE3: Not sure, but I met the druid once. I was riding through the Moors, minding my own business, when he came up and spoke in the beast-tongue.

9137706E.Line5.CDDE3: I don’t care what happened between them. I’m just glad Donan came to his senses and broke it off with that brute.

F742F6EC.Line3.CDDE3: Caused my horse to throw me. I broke my leg. Hasn’t been the same since.
